title: Pink T-34 Stompie
description:
Soviet-era battle tank painted pink in the centre of the city. No kidding, that's a whole story behind the thing: the owner of the land wasn't allowed to build the desired building on the site so he just placed the T-34 in the place its gun facing the roadway
Теперь и в розовом цвете.

title: Eroma
description: Good sandwich bar/internet cafe. Jacket Potatoes highly recommended

title: Ollie's Foods
description: 24hour supermarket, eternally useful. Nice bread. Lovely collection of olives. Lovely people, not sure if they are Turkish, Arab or Kurdish though (not that it makes a difference)

title: DRS Construction workshops
description:
DRS Construction builds Film and Television scenery from this railway arch.
Many small businesses lease the brick vaulted arches of the rail viaducts which offer
reasonably secure, if slightly troglodyte accommodation at low cost
